Users:

POST /api/users/register - Opret bruger
http://localhost:3000/api/users/register
{
    "name": "Anders Andersen",
    "email": "anders@test.dk",
    "password": "password123",
    "profile": {
        "age": 28,
        "weight": 82,
        "height": 185,
        "gender": "male",
        "fitnessGoal": "strength"
    }
}

POST /api/users/login - Login
http://localhost:3000/api/users/login
{
    "email": "anders@test.dk",
    "password": "password123"
}

GET /api/users/:id - Hent bruger
http://localhost:3000/api/users/ID

PUT /api/users/:id - Opdater bruger
http://localhost:3000/api/users/ID
{
    "name": "Anders Nielsen",
    "profile": {
        "age": 29,
        "weight": 85,
        "height": 185,
        "gender": "male",
        "fitnessGoal": "musclebuild-up"
    }
}

DELETE /api/users/:id - Slet bruger
http://localhost:3000/api/users/ID

Workout Plans:
POST /api/workout-plans - Opret plan
http://localhost:3000/api/workout-plans
{
    "user": "user id",
    "name": "Begynder Styrkeprogram",
    "description": "3 dages træningsprogram for begyndere",
    "workoutType": "strength",
    "exercises": [
        {
            "exerciseName": "Bænkpres",
            "sets": 3,
            "reps": 10,
            "restTime": 90,
            "notes": "Hold albuerne ind"
        },
        {
            "exerciseName": "Squat",
            "sets": 4,
            "reps": 8,
            "restTime": 120,
            "notes": "Gå til parallel"
        },
        {
            "exerciseName": "Dødløft",
            "sets": 3,
            "reps": 5,
            "restTime": 180,
            "notes": "Hold ryggen lige"
        }
    ]
}
GET /api/workout-plans/user/:userId - Hent brugers planer
http://localhost:3000/api/workout-plans/user/ID

GET /api/workout-plans/:id - Hent én plan
http://localhost:3000/api/workout-plans/ID

PUT /api/workout-plans/:id - Opdater plan
http://localhost:3000/api/workout-plans/ID
{
    "user": "user id",
    "name": "Avanceret Styrkeprogram",
    "description": "4 dages program med progressiv overload",
